{
  "stem": "4963.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And again, I, later on, when-- in our store-- and our house was converted into a headquarters for the secret police.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was always very self-sufficient, really born to be a survivor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I knew, I thought I knew what I wanted, you know, and I wanted independence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to do my own thinking and do my own thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I was really very stubborn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember that my parents would say that they went through all the governesses-- in Lithuania they had to import them because I just didn't want anybody to follow me in school and everywhere I went, they would have to follow me and see what I'm doing and whom I'm playing with, and so I'd make their life so miserable that they would-- that they would leave.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they'd have to bring other ones in from all around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So how it affected me, well, at first, I really thought, since I always dreamt of being independent as a child, and I'd say why do I need somebody to follow me and tell me what to do?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I would say, one day, I'm going to run away from-- from home, and-- or I wish I didn't have anybody, any parents, to-- to tell me what to do and how to do.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when the war started, I really-- or-- well, the-- when the Germans came in, I went to a camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just before the Germans came, I went to a summer camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, again, against my parents' wishes, because they knew that-- that our-- they-- they used to take the wealthy people, send them out to Siberia to get rid of them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, word went around that this will happen, that they would be sent out.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
